divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving on 50 hwy in Lee's Summit MO and saw what looked like 2 x shaped things with lights on them almost flying connected to each other or overlapping or just really close to each other than it looked like they turned a kind of sharp circle almost like how a leaf falls in a circle but didn't fall or anything, but then it almost looked like either the lights turned off or it dissappeared or something but before I could tell if it was just the angle or what, I had driven out of the line of sight. I don't really believe in aliens, I don't think, but it was definitely an unidentified flying object whether that makes it some military plane or what.
